69b65aeb-4140-4c8d-851a-ecab118befcd.name: namespace
69b65aeb-4140-4c8d-851a-ecab118befcd.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'namespace') AS namespace
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4_1day
WHERE (metric_name = 'temporal_request') AND (unix_milli >= (toUnixTimestamp(now() - toIntervalDay(1)) * 1000))
GROUP BY namespace
